---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const title = "Disclaimer | Des Moines Septic";
const description = "Disclaimer for desmoinesseptic.com.";
---
<Layout {title} {description}>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:820px">
      <h1>Disclaimer</h1>
      <p><em>Last updated: May 2026</em></p>
      <p>The information on this website is provided by Des Moines Septic for general informational purposes about septic systems, services, pricing, and Iowa regulations affecting septic system owners in the Des Moines metro.</p>
      <h2>Informational Content</h2>
      <p>Content on this website, including service descriptions, price ranges, maintenance tips, and FAQ answers, is provided for general informational purposes. Septic system specifics vary by tank, soil, system age, county code, and other factors. For binding advice about your specific system, rely on the inspection and recommendations we provide after assessing your property.</p>
      <h2>Pricing Disclaimer</h2>
      <p>Price ranges shown reflect typical residential service in the Des Moines metro at time of publication. Final pricing is confirmed by phone before any work is performed. We do not guarantee specific prices without first assessing the property and the scope of service required.</p>
      <h2>Licensing</h2>
      <p>Des Moines Septic maintains current Iowa septage hauler licensing, Iowa Time of Transfer inspector certification (administered through IOWWA, the Iowa Onsite Waste Water Association, under Iowa DNR rules), and liability insurance. Specific license numbers and insurance certificates are available on request.</p>
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions about this disclaimer? Call (515) 303-4896 or use our <a href="/contact/">contact form</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
